    <p><b>View result from shared link:</b></p>

    <p>
        This option lets you paste your result link
        to see its chart. If someone shares a link to you, you need to enter that link
        here to see the chart.
    </p>

    <p>
        Please note that this is a link to a JSON
        file, so CSV links will not work here.
    </p>

    <p>
        <img width=752 height=258 id="Picture 9"
             src="help/image012.jpg">
    </p>

    <p>&nbsp;</p>

    <p><b>Upload Monica result file:</b></p>

    <p>
        If you have saved your result before, you
        can drop it anytime here to see it on a chart. Old results (only in JSON format)
        should also work fine.
    </p>

